# Flutter Rules — WonderLens

## Dart conventions

- Null-safety bắt buộc — không dùng `!` trừ khi chắc chắn non-null
- Tên file: `snake_case.dart`
- Class: `PascalCase`
- Variable/method: `camelCase`

## Architecture

- State management: **Riverpod** (đã chọn, xem ADR-001)
- KHÔNG thêm bloc, redux, mobx
- Business logic KHÔNG viết trong widget → tách ra `services/` hoặc `notifiers/`
- Widget lớn (> ~100 dòng) → tách file riêng trong `lib/widgets/`

## File structure

```
lib/
├── screens/      # Screen widgets (camera, timeline, collection)
├── widgets/      # Reusable widgets
├── services/     # Business logic (recognition, content, narration, collection)
├── models/       # Data models + Hive entities
├── providers/    # Riverpod providers
└── main.dart
```

## Camera lifecycle (critical)

- Luôn check `mounted` sau mọi `await` trước khi gọi `setState`
- Dispose `CameraController` trong `dispose()`
- Handle background/resume: reinit camera khi app resume
- Không race condition khi init

```dart
// Đúng:
await _controller.initialize();
if (!mounted) return;
setState(() { _isInitialized = true; });
```

## Assets

- Content hero: `assets/content/{object_id}.json`
- Audio: `assets/audio/{object_id}_stage{n}.mp3`
- Video: `assets/videos/{object_id}_making.mp4`
- Poster: `assets/images/{object_id}_video_poster.png`
- Trường `video` là optional — check null trước khi load

## Proxy calls

- KHÔNG gọi OpenAI trực tiếp
- Timeout: 10s cho recognize, 30s cho generate
- Luôn handle error gracefully (toast, không crash)

## Tests

- Unit test cho: `recognition_service`, `content_service`, `collection_service`
- Widget test cho: `TimelineScreen`, `CollectionScreen`
- Chạy `flutter test` trước push
